ont-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">索引节点：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">又称<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">i</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">节点，在文件系统中包含有关文件的信息的一个记录，包含文件权限、属主、大小、位置、日期等。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">数据：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">文件的实际内容，它可以是空的，也可以非常大，并且有自己的结构。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">文件名</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">尽量简单</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">最长可多达<span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">255</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个字符</span></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';\">区分大小写</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5pt;ms