t: 0px; \">\r\n		-T或--print-type&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示文件系统的类型。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		du 显示目录或文件的大小</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a或-all&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示目录中个别文件的大小</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-h以K，M，G为单位，提高信息的可读性</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-s或--summarize&nbsp;&nbsp; 仅显示总计</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-S 显示个别目录的大小时，并不含其子目录的大小</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-k或--kilobytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 以1024 bytes为单位</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-m或--megabytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 以1MB为单位</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<br />\r\n		fdisk<br />\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 命令行工具，各种版本和环境都能用</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<strong>6.3、分区格式化</strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		mkfs -t ext3 /dev/sda6<br />\r\n		mkfs&nbsp;<br />\r\n		-t vfat /dev/sda5<br />\r\n		mkfs.ext3 /dev/sda6</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<strong>6.4、检验</strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		fsck [-t&nbsp; 文件系统] [ACay] 设备名</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-t : 给定档案系统的型式，若在 /etc/fstab 中已有定义或 kernel 本身已支援的则不需加上此参数 　　　</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-A : 对/etc/fstab 中所有列出来的 partition 做检查</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-C : 显示完整的检查进度 　　</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a : 如果检查有错则自动修复 　　</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-r : 如果检查有错则由使用者回答是否修复</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-f:强制检验</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		fsck -C -f -t ext3 /dev/sda6</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		fsck [tab] [tab]</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.5、挂载、自动挂载<br />\r\n		挂载的意义</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<strong>6.5、挂载、自动挂载</strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		mount -a<br />\r\n		mount -l<br />\r\n		mount [-t vfstype] [-o options] device dir</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a 依照配置文件/etc/fstab挂载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-l 列出挂载信息</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-L 可以指定卷标名挂载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-o 后接额外参数：</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount /dev/sdb1 /mnt/s1</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -t iso9660 /dev/cdrom /media/cdrom</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mkfs -t vfat /dev/fd0</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -t vfat /dev/fd0/media/floppy</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -t vfat -o iocharset=cp950 /dev/sda1 /u</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#cp /dev/cdrom /home/mydisk.iso</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#dd if=/dev/cdrom of=/home/mydisk.iso</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -o loop&nbsp; /home/mydisk.iso /mnt/vcdrom</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount 10.0.0.1:/var/ftp/put /mnt</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		umount [-fn] 设备名或挂载点</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-f强卸载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-n不更新/etc/mtab情况下卸载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<strong>6.6、创建交换空间（swap）</strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step1:分一个分区</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step2:mkswap /dev/sdc8</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step3:swapon /dev/hdc7</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		free<br />\r\n		查看swap内存</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		swapon -s查看</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<strong>6.6、创建交换空间（swap）</strong></p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		创建swap文件</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step1：dd if=/dev/zero of=/tmp/swap bs=1M count=128</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step2: mkswap /tmp/swap</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step3: swapon /tem/swap</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		swapoff /tmp/swap</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		swapoff /dev/sdc8</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'show_course',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/aq3f8ds4# ch06磁盘相关操作_01.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \' ch06磁盘相关操作_01.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★★☆☆','VIP'),
 (34,'<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font: normal normal normal 12px/1.5 \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; \">\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.1、硬盘与Linux文件系统</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		硬盘组成</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		(盘片、马达、机械手、磁头、扇区、柱面）</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		硬盘分区</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		ext2文件系统</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.2、磁盘分区</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		df 磁盘信息</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a或--all&nbsp;&nbsp; 包含全部的文件系统。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-h以可读性较高的方式来显示信息。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-i或--inodes&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示inode的信息。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-k或--kilobytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 指定区块大小为1024字节。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-l或--local&nbsp;&nbsp; 仅显示本地端的文件系统。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-T或--print-type&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示文件系统的类型。</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		du 显示目录或文件的大小</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a或-all&nbsp;&nbsp; 显示目录中个别文件的大小</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-h以K，M，G为单位，提高信息的可读性</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-s或--summarize&nbsp;&nbsp; 仅显示总计</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-S 显示个别目录的大小时，并不含其子目录的大小</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-k或--kilobytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 以1024 bytes为单位</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-m或--megabytes&nbsp;&nbsp; 以1MB为单位</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		<br />\r\n		fdisk<br />\r\n		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 命令行工具，各种版本和环境都能用</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.3、分区格式化</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		mkfs -t ext3 /dev/sda6<br />\r\n		mkfs&nbsp;<br />\r\n		-t vfat /dev/sda5<br />\r\n		mkfs.ext3 /dev/sda6</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.4、检验</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		fsck [-t&nbsp; 文件系统] [ACay] 设备名</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-t : 给定档案系统的型式，若在 /etc/fstab 中已有定义或 kernel 本身已支援的则不需加上此参数 　　　</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-A : 对/etc/fstab 中所有列出来的 partition 做检查</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-C : 显示完整的检查进度 　　</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a : 如果检查有错则自动修复 　　</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-r : 如果检查有错则由使用者回答是否修复</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-f:强制检验</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		fsck -C -f -t ext3 /dev/sda6</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		fsck [tab] [tab]</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.5、挂载、自动挂载<br />\r\n		挂载的意义</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.5、挂载、自动挂载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		mount -a<br />\r\n		mount -l<br />\r\n		mount [-t vfstype] [-o options] device dir</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-a 依照配置文件/etc/fstab挂载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-l 列出挂载信息</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-L 可以指定卷标名挂载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-o 后接额外参数：</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount /dev/sdb1 /mnt/s1</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -t iso9660 /dev/cdrom /media/cdrom</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mkfs -t vfat /dev/fd0</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -t vfat /dev/fd0/media/floppy</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -t vfat -o iocharset=cp950 /dev/sda1 /u</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#cp /dev/cdrom /home/mydisk.iso</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#dd if=/dev/cdrom of=/home/mydisk.iso</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount -o loop&nbsp; /home/mydisk.iso /mnt/vcdrom</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		#mount 10.0.0.1:/var/ftp/put /mnt</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		umount [-fn] 设备名或挂载点</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-f强卸载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		-n不更新/etc/mtab情况下卸载</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.6、创建交换空间（swap）</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step1:分一个分区</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step2:mkswap /dev/sdc8</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step3:swapon /dev/hdc7</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		free<br />\r\n		查看swap内存</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		swapon -s查看</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		6.6、创建交换空间（swap）</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		创建swap文件</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step1：dd if=/dev/zero of=/tmp/swap bs=1M count=128</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step2: mkswap /tmp/swap</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		step3: swapon /tem/swap</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		swapoff /tmp/swap</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		swapoff /dev/sdc8</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'show_course',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/e6ul1b43#ch_06磁盘相关操作_02.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch_06磁盘相关操作_02.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★★☆☆','VIP'),
