ttp://www.skycn.com/soft/51840.html</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"layout\">\r\n	下载地址（pchome）：<a href=\"http://download.pchome.net/development/sever/php/detail-40373.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#136ec2;\">http://download.pchome.net/development/sever/php/detail-40373.html</span></a></p>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'show_course',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/clghf3iy# ch3_phpStudy安装WordPress_2.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch3_phpStudy安装WordPress_2.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','共享'),
