 style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;padding-top:0px;\">\r\n	<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"line-height:24px;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:宋体;\"><b style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;padding-top:0px;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">TCP SYN扫描&nbsp;</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;padding-top:0px;\">\r\n	<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"line-height:24px;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:宋体;\"><b style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;padding-top:0px;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 发送SYN数据包收到SYN|ACK的返回信息表示端口处于侦听状态。一个RST返回，表示端口没有处于侦听态。如果收到一个SYN|ACK，则扫描程序必须再发送一个RST信号，来关闭这个连接过程。</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;padding-top:0px;\">\r\n	<span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"line-height:24px;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:宋体;\"><b style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;padding-top:0px;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">TCP FIN 扫描&nbsp;</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;border-right-width:0px;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;pa