y: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">同样的，<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Context.bindServies()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">可以让调用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">的元素和</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">直接建立关联（如果</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">没有启动，则可选去启动该</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">onBind()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来获取</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Intents</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">。如果一个</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Activity</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">可以启动一个</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">用来</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">music</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">回放并提供一个界面给用户，以便用户操作回放过程。该关联可以通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Context.bindServies()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来建立。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">RPC<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">将有更详细的介绍。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">Broadcast:&nbsp;Context.sendBroadcast()<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Context.sendorderedBroadcast()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Context.sendStickyBroadcast()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">，均可以通过传递一个</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Intent</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来发起一个</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">BroadCast</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Android</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">onReceive()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">将</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Intent</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">传递给所有对该</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Broadcast</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">感兴趣的</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">broadcast</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">接收者。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \">(二)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \">元素的去激活</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">Content&nbsp;provider<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">仅仅在响应</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Content&nbsp;Revolver</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">的请求时才激活；</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Broadcast&nbsp;receiver</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">在响应广播时才激活，因此，该两种元素没有显示的去激活。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">Activity<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">和</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Services:</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">提供用户界面或者是后台运行，可能长时间保持激活状态，即便在</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">IDLE</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">状态下，仍然有可能和用户交互。因此需要有方法将其去激活：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">1.Activity<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">可以通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">finish()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">方法实现去激活。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Activity&nbsp;A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">可以通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">finishActivity</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来去激活</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Activity&nbsp;B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">，前提，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Activity&nbsp;B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">是通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">startActivityForResult()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来激活的。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">2.&nbsp;Services<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">可通过调用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">stopSelt()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来实现去激活，或者调用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Context.stopService()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">此外，当该元素不再被使用或者系统要求释放内存给其他元素使用时，系统会去激活该元素。详细描述，见元素生命周期。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \">(三)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \">Manifest<span style=\"font-family: 黑体; \">文件</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">在<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">android</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">启动一个应用之前，它必须知道该应用元素是否存在。因此，应用程序将自身的元素描述在一个</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">manifest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件中并将其打入到</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">apk</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">包中，即</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">*.apk</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件，该文件中包含应用的代码，资源文件，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">manifest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件等。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">Manifest<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件是</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">xml</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">格式。总是命名为</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">AndroidManifest.xml</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">，每个应用一个，并保存在应用的根目录下。它的作用是描述应用的元素，还包括应用必须</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Link</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">的库（</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Android</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">缺省的库除外），许可设置等。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">该文件的主要目的还是描述应用的元素。例如：</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&lt;?xml&nbsp;version=&quot;1.0&quot;&nbsp;encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&lt;manifest&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;application&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;activity&nbsp;android:name=&quot;com.example.project.FreneticActivity&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;android:icon=&quot;@drawable/small_pic.png&quot;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;android:label=&quot;@string/freneticLabel&quot;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/activity&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/application&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">&lt;/manifest&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">该文件描述的是<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Activity</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">元素，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">name</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">对应名称，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Icon</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">和</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">label</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">指向资源文件，该资源文件包含了显示给用户看的</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">ICON</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">和</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">LABEL</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">Service<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">元素的描述也是类似的，使用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">&lt;services&gt;..&lt;/services&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">；</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">broadcast&nbsp;receivers</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">&lt;receiver&gt;...&lt;/receiver&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来描述</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">;&nbsp;content&nbsp;providers</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">使用</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">&lt;provider&gt;...&lt;/provider&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来描述。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">如果元素没有在<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Manifest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件中进行描述，则系统对其不可见，即永远不会运行。但是，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">broadcast&nbsp;receiver</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">是例外，该元素可以在</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Manifest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件中进行描述，也可以在代码中通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">BroadcastReceiver</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">对象来动态产生，并通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Context.registerReceiver()</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">来注册到系统。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \">(四)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \">Intent&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 黑体; \">筛选</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; \"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: 10.5pt; \">一个<span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Intent</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">对象实例可以显示地指定目的元素，该情况下，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Android</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">将通过</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">manifest</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">文件中的描述来寻找该元素，并激活它。如果没有显示地指定元素，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Android</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">必须定位到最合适的元素以便处理</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Intent</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; \">。一个元素的</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; \">Intent</sp