 (84,'<p>\r\n	这一节学习ImageView、ImageButton、Gallery的用法</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		ImageView（图片控件）</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		ImageButton（图片按纽组件）</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		Gallery（图片滑动组件）</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'show_course',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/e6uz8ztd# ch16_Android常用控件_05.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch16_Android常用控件_05.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (85,'<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font: normal normal normal 12px/1.5 \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; \">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong>17.1 ProgressBar</strong></div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		长形进度条progressBarStyleHorizontal</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		圆形进度条progressBarStyleLarge</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		标题栏进度requestWindowFeature(Window.FEATURE_PROGRESS);</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		setMax()设置进度条最大值</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		setProgress()设置进度条当前值</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		setVisibility()设置进度条可见</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			<strong>17.2 SeekBar</strong></div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			拖动条，类似一下进度条，只是人可以控制进度</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			SeekBar的事件监听为</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			SeekBar.OnSeekBarChangeListener接口</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			三个方法：</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			onProgressChanged数值改变</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			onStartTrackingTouch开始拖动</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			onStopTrackingTouch停止拖动</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			<strong>17.3 Notification</strong></div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Toast Notification</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Status Bar Notification</div>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Dialog Notification</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong>17.4 grid_view</strong></div>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'show_course',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/aqkur9i2# ch17_Android常用控件_06(1).zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch17_Android常用控件_06(1).zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (86,'<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	18.1View<br />\r\n	View是所有组件的超类<br />\r\n	每个View都有一个绘画的画布<br />\r\n	我们可以任意扩展画布<br />\r\n	任可一个View都可以重写onDraw方法来决定View的显示<br />\r\n	View提供了onKeyUp、onKeyDown、onTouchEvent等方法来响应用户操作<br />\r\n	invalidate方法来实现界面刷新，不能直接在线程中调用，这些操作必须在UI线程中执行<br />\r\n	Androi常用Handler来实现UI线程更新<br />\r\n	postInvalidate也可以更新界面，不再需要Handler</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	18.2 SurfaceView<br />\r\n	View都是在相同的GUI线程中绘制，主应用程序线程同时也用来处理所有的用户交互<br />\r\n	View不允许后台线程对期更新<br />\r\n	当需要快速地更新View的UI，可以选择SurfaceView<br />\r\n	SurfaceView封装了一个Surface对象，而不是Canvas<br />\r\n	因为Surface可以使用后台线程绘制，而View不能</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	何时应该使用SurfaceView？<br />\r\n	SurfaceView使用的方式与任何View所派生的类都是完全相同的。可以像其他View那样应用动画，并把它们放到布局中。<br />\r\n	SurfaceView封装的Surface支持所有标准Canvas方法进行绘图，同时也支持完全的OpenGL ES库。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	创建一个新的SurfaceView控件<br />\r\n	要创建一个新的SurfaceView，需要创建一个新的扩展了SurfaceView的类，并实现SurfaceHolder.Callback。<br />\r\n	surfaceHolder回调可以在底层的Surface被创建和销毁的时候通知View，并传递给它对SurfaceHolder对象的引用，其中包含了当前有效的Surface。<br />\r\n	一个典型的Surface View设计模型包括一个由Thread所派生的类，它可以接收对当前的SurfaceHolder的引用，并独立地更新它。<br />\r\n	SurfaceHolder.Callback接口<br />\r\n	surfaceChanged:surface大小改变<br />\r\n	surfaceCreated：创建Surface<br />\r\n	surfaceDestroyed:销毁surface</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	通过getHolder()得到SurfaceHolder对象<br />\r\n	addCallback:给surfaceView添加一个回调函数<br />\r\n	lockCanvas:锁定画布，得到画布<br />\r\n	unlockCanvasAndPost解锁画布<br />\r\n	removeCallback：从SurfaceView中移除回调函数</p>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/e6uz8w1i# ch18_android组件重绘_01.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch18_android组件重绘_01.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (87,'<p>\r\n	这一节学习,几何图形的绘制、图像的绘制及缩放和旋转</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	&nbsp;19.1 Paint</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setAntiAlias:设置画笔的锯齿效果</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setColor:设置画笔的颜色</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setARGB:设置画笔的a,r,g,b值</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setTextSize:设置字体的大小</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setStyle:设置画笔的风格，空心或实心</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setStrokeWidth:设置空心的边框宽度</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	getColor得到画笔的颜色</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	getAlpha得到画笔的Alpha值</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	19.1 Canvas</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	drawColor:设置Canvas的背景颜色</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setBitmap：设置具体画布</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	clipRect:设置显示区域（裁剪区）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	isOpaque:检测是否支持透明</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	rotate：旋转画布</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n	setViewport：设置画布中显示窗口</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		几何图形绘制</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawRect &nbsp; 绘制矩形</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawCircle 绘制圆形</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawOval &nbsp; 绘制椭圆</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawPath &nbsp;绘制任意多边形</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawLine &nbsp;绘制直线</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawPoint 绘制点</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		drawText绘制字符串</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		绘制图像</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		取得图像资源</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Bitmap &nbsp;bitmap=((Bitmap)getResources().getDrawable(图像资源)).getBitmap();</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		canvas.drawBitmap(bitmap,x,y,null);</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		图像旋转、缩放</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Matrix matrix=new Matrix();</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		matrix.reset();</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		matrix.setRotate(0.0f);</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		matrix.setpostScale(1.0f,1.0f);</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Bitmap bitmap=Bitmap.createBitmap(bitmat,0,0,100,50,matrix,true);</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		canvas.drawBitmap(bitmap,x,y,null);</div>\r\n</div>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/aq3h09qf# ch19_android组件重绘_02.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch19_android组件重绘_02.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (88,'<p><strong>第一部分：网页开发</strong><br />\r\nhttp协议、html、DW、css、div+CSS、JS、JQuery<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>第二部分：程序开发</strong><br />\r\napache、PHP基础、正则表达式、面向对象、文件操作、mysqli、PDO、Smarty、MySQL<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>第三部分：网站案例</strong><br />\r\nphpcms二次开发、wordpress二次开发<br />\r\n网站系统开发<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>第四部分：服务器搭建</strong><br />\r\nlinux、web服务、邮件服务、Ftp服务、DNS服务..<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>第五部分：高并发高性能WEB架构</strong><br />\r\n动态内容缓存、web服务器缓存、反向代理缓存、分布式缓存、数据库性能优化、Mysql复制与集群、共享文件系统、分布式文件系统、分布式计算、性能监控<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>第六部分：网站推广</strong></p>\r\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"ke-flash\" kesrc=\"http://www.redwww.com/uploadfile/2012/0101/20120101120932897.gif\" kesrctag=\"%3Cembed%20height%3D%22490%22%20type%3D%22application/x-shockwave-flash%22%20width%3D%22650%22%20src%3D%22http%3A//www.docin.com/DocinViewer-260982653-144.swf%22%20allowscriptaccess%3D%22always%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%22true%22%20/%3E\" src=\"http://www.redwww.com/uploadfile/2012/0101/20120101120932897.gif\" style=\"width: 650px; height: 490px\" /> ',0,'',0,10000,'show_course',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/aqy2h3ro#ch01_网站开发与运营课程简介.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch01_网站开发与运营课程简介.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★☆☆☆☆','共享'),
 (89,'<span style=\"line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; white-space: normal\">Fireworks是一个轻量的图形处理软件，而且是矢量的，最适合用在互联网了，所以麦哥这一节把自己平时使用Fireworks的经验给大家做个分享，总的来说这种软件操作性很强，技巧性也很强，所以大家一定多练习哦</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px\">Fireworks是Macromedia公司发布的一款专为网络</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/42121.htm\" style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(19,110,194); font-size: 14px\" target=\"_blank\">图形</a><span style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px\">设计的图形编辑软件，它大大</span>\r\n<div class=\"text_pic\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(232,232,232) 1px solid; position: relative; text-align: center; border-left: rgb(232,232,232) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 3px; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); margin: 5px; padding-left: 5px; width: 120px; padding-right: 5px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; float: right; visibility: visible; font-size: 14px; border-top: rgb(232,232,232) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(232,232,232) 1px solid; padding-top: 5px; border-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial\"><a class=\"pic-handle\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/albums/23262/23262.html#0$246cca2a0bc22fb2023bf604\" style=\"background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/baike/bk-split-icons.png); border-bottom: rgb(246,246,246) 1px solid; position: absolute; border-left: rgb(246,246,246) 1px solid; line-height: 0; width: 14px; bottom: 4px; display: block; background-position: 0px 0px; height: 14px; color: rgb(19,110,194); font-size: 0px; border-top: rgb(246,246,246) 1px solid; right: 4px; border-right: rgb(246,246,246) 1px solid; text-decoration: none; border-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"查看图片\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/albums/23262/23262.html#0$246cca2a0bc22fb2023bf604\" style=\"color: rgb(19,110,194)\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"editorImg log-set-param\" log-set-param=\"img_view\" src=\"http://www.redwww.com/uploadfile/2012/0101/20120101121606588.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; display: block; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-image: initial\" title=\"Adobe Firework CS4\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pic-info\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px; margin: 3px 0px 0px; min-height: 18px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 10px; zoom: 1; display: inline; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 12px; word-break: break-all; padding-top: 0px\">Adobe Firework CS4</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px\">简 化了网络图形设计的工作难度，无论是专业设计家还是业余爱好者，使用Fireworks都不仅可以轻松地制作出十分动感的GIF</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/7262.htm\" style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(19,110,194); font-size: 14px\" target=\"_blank\">动画</a><span style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px\">，还可以轻易地完成大图切割、动态按钮、动态翻转图等，因此，对于辅助</span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/828.htm\" style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(19,110,194); font-size: 14px\" target=\"_blank\">网页</a><span style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 14px\">编辑来说，Fireworks将是最大的功臣。借助于 Macromedia Fireworks 8，您可以在直观、可定制的环境中创建和优化用于网页的图像并进行精确控制