 (114,'<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.1PHPCMS建站的步骤</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">第一步：网站功能定制<br />\r\n第二步：UI设计到HTML模型<br />\r\n第三步：新建PHPCMS模板<br />\r\n第四步：将PHPCMS标签加入HTML模板中</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.2PHPCMS目录结构</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">根目录<br />\r\n| &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;api &nbsp;结构文件目录<br />\r\n| &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;caches 缓存文件目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; configs 系统配置文件目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; caches_* 系统缓存目录<br />\r\n| &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;phpcms &nbsp;phpcms框架主目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; languages 框架语言包目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; libs 框架主类库、主函数库目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; model 框架数据库模型目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; modules 框架模块目录<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; templates 框架系统模板目录<br />\r\n| &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;phpsso_server &nbsp;phpsso主目录<br />\r\n| &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;statics &nbsp;系统附件包<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; css 系统css包<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; images 系统图片包<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; | &nbsp;&ndash; js 系统js包<br />\r\n| &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;index.php &nbsp;程序主入口</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.3PHPCMS静态资源</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">常用变量<br />\r\n/statics/css&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {CSS_PATH}<br />\r\n/statics/images&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {IMG_PATH}<br />\r\n/statics/js&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; {JS_PATH}</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.4PHPCMS模板语法规则</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">1、变量表示<br />\r\n{$name} 被解析成 &lt;?=$name?&gt;<br />\r\n2、常量表示<br />\r\n{name}被解析成&lt;?=name?&gt;<br />\r\n3、条件判断<br />\r\n{if *} * {else} * {else} * {/if}<br />\r\n4、循环<br />\r\n{loop $a $b} * {/loop} 或者 {loop $a $b $c} * {/loop} ，{loop $a $b} * {/loop}<br />\r\n被解析成&lt;?php if(is_array($a)) foreach($a AS $b) { ?&gt; * &lt;?php } ?&gt;<br />\r\n5.模板包含<br />\r\n{template &#39;module name&#39;,&#39;file name&#39;}</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">参考：<a href=\"http://v9.help.phpcms.cn/html/2011/yufa_0520/110.html\" kesrc=\"http://v9.help.phpcms.cn/html/2011/yufa_0520/110.html\">http://v9.help.phpcms.cn/html/2011/yufa_0520/110.html</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.5PHPCMS PC标签</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">PHPCMS v9中主要用pc标签来取数据<br />\r\nPC标签说明<br />\r\n&nbsp; ｛pc:content action=&quot;lists&quot; cache=&quot;3600&quot; num=&quot;20&quot; page=&quot;$page&quot;｝{/pc}<br />\r\nPC标签保留参数<br />\r\naction&nbsp;&nbsp; 所做的操作&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 默认值 null<br />\r\ncache&nbsp;&nbsp; 缓存时间&nbsp;&nbsp; 单位秒&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 默认值&nbsp; 0<br />\r\nnum&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 所取的数据量&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 默认值&nbsp; 20<br />\r\npage&nbsp;&nbsp; 分页变量&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 默认值 null<br />\r\nreturn&nbsp; 返回值&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 默认值 data</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.5PHPCMS PC标签</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">{pc:content action=&quot;lists&quot; catid=&quot;25&quot; num=&quot;20&quot; page=&quot;$_GET[page]&quot; return=&quot;data&quot;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;ul&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;{loop $data $n $r}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;{$r[url]}&quot;&gt;{$r[title]}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;{/loop}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;/ul&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;{/pc}</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.6PHPCMS 其它常用标签</strong><br />\r\n截取调用标题长度&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n{str_cut($r[title],36,&#39;&#39;)}<br />\r\n格式化时间<br />\r\n{date(&#39;Y-m-d H:i:s&#39;,$r[inputtime])}<br />\r\n显示栏目名<br />\r\n&lt;ahref=&quot;{$CATEGORYS[$r[catid]][url]}&quot;&gt;{$CATEGORYS[$r[&#39;catid&#39;]][&#39;catname&#39;]}&lt;/a&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;获取父栏目id/获取父栏目名称<br />\r\n{$CATEGORY[$catid][parentid]}<br />\r\n&nbsp;{$CATEGORYS[$CAT[parentid]][catname]}<br />\r\n调用子栏目<br />\r\n{pc:content action=&quot;category&quot; catid=&quot;$catid&quot; num=&quot;25&quot; siteid=&quot;$siteid&quot; order=&quot;listorder ASC&quot;}<br />\r\n{loop $data $r}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;{$r[url]}&quot;&gt;{$r[catname]}&lt;/a&gt; |<br />\r\n{/loop}<br />\r\n{/pc}<br />\r\n显示指定id的栏目名称 （例子这里catid=22)<br />\r\n{$CATEGORYS[22][&#39;catname&#39;]}</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>9.7PHPCMS get标签</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">GET标签源自于PHPCMS 2008版，其使用SQL语句直接获取数据的特性，成为大家制作模板的首选。<br />\r\n在V9中这样强大的工具也得到保留下来。<br />\r\n{pc:get sql=&quot;SELECT * FROM phpcms_member&quot; cache=&quot;3600&quot; page=&quot;$page&quot; dbsource=&quot;discuz&quot; return=&quot;data&quot;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;ul&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;{loop $data $key $val}<br />\r\n&nbsp;{$val[username]}&lt;br /&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;{/loop}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;/ul&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;{$pages}<br />\r\n&nbsp;{/pc}</p>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/aqv5zeff#ch09_PHPCMS模板开发(1).zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch09_PHPCMS模板开发(1).zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (115,'<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">&nbsp;PHP（&ldquo;PHP: Hypertext Preprocessor&rdquo;）的缩写<br />\r\n开放源码，嵌入HTML中的脚本语言，更适合WEB<br />\r\n混合了 C、Java、Perl 以及 PHP 自创新的语法<br />\r\n比 CGI或者Perl更快速的执行动态网页<br />\r\n可以运行在UNIX、LINUX、WINDOWS下<br />\r\n在php4,php5 中，面向对象方面都有了很大的改进，现在php完全可以用来开发大型商业程序<br />\r\nPHP可以完成任何CGI能做的事情<br />\r\n命令行脚本<br />\r\n编写桌面应用程序</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>step1:安装apache2.2<br />\r\nstep2:安装php5.2</strong><br />\r\n1、还原php.ini<br />\r\n2、将php目录和php/ext加入环境变量path<br />\r\n3、在apache/conf/httpd.conf中配置php模块<br />\r\nLoadModule php5_module &quot;c:/php/php5apache2_2.dll&quot;<br />\r\nAddType application/x-httpd-php .php<br />\r\nPHPIniDir &quot;C:/php&quot;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>step3:安装mysql扩展</strong><br />\r\n修改php.ini<br />\r\nextension=php_mysql.dll<br />\r\nextension=php_mysqli.dll<br />\r\n将php安装目录下的libmysql.dll放入c:\\windows目录<br />\r\n<strong>step4:安装Zend加速器<br />\r\nstep5:测试</strong></p>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/bhkhztrt#ch10_PHP开发环境搭建.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch10_PHP开发环境搭建.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (116,'<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><strong>11.1 PHP标记</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">默认语法<br />\r\n&lt;?php&nbsp; ... ?&gt;<br />\r\n短标记（需要在php.ini中开启short_open_tag），会与xml冲突<br />\r\n&lt;? ... ?&gt;<br />\r\n脚本<br />\r\n&lt;script language=&quot;php&quot;&gt; ... &lt;/script&gt;<br />\r\nASP风格（需要开启asp_tag=On）<br />\r\n&lt;% ... %&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">PHP标记嵌入HTML中<br />\r\nhtml标签内可以嵌入php标记<br />\r\nbody标记的任何位置<br />\r\nhtml可做为php的语句体</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><br />\r\n<strong>11.2 注释</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">C/C++格式的注册<br />\r\n//注释内容<br />\r\n/*<br />\r\n多行注释内容<br />\r\n*/<br />\r\nshell格式的注释<br />\r\n#单行注释</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><br />\r\n<strong>11.3 数据输出</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">int print(argument)<br />\r\n&lt;?php<br />\r\nprint(&quot;&lt;p&gt;I love php&lt;/p&gt;&quot;);<br />\r\n?&gt;<br />\r\nvoid echo(string arg1[,... argn])<br />\r\n&lt;?php<br />\r\n&nbsp; echo &quot;echo输出，和println一样&lt;br/&gt;&quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp; $a=&quot;hello&quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp; $b=&quot;angel&quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp; echo $a,&quot;&nbsp; &quot;,$b,&quot;!&lt;br/&gt;&quot; ;<br />\r\n?&gt;<br />\r\nboolean printf(string format[,mixed args])<br />\r\nprint(&quot;hi %s&quot;,&quot;zhangsan&quot;);<br />\r\nstring sprintf(string format[,mixed args])<br />\r\n的printf一样，只是sprint输出到字符串<br />\r\n$cost=sprintf(&quot;$%.2f&quot;,43.2);<br />\r\n参考：ch11/demo4.php<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>11.4 标识符</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">定义变量、函数和其他各种用户定义对象通用的术语<br />\r\n必须以字母或下划线开头，由字母、数字、下划线组成<br />\r\n区分大小写<br />\r\n长度任意<br />\r\n不能是php的关键字<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>11.5 变量</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">以$后跟标识符表示<br />\r\nphp中的变量不要求在使用前声明<br />\r\n第一次给变量赋值时才创建这个变量<br />\r\n$a=10;<br />\r\n$b=&quot;hello&quot;;<br />\r\n$c=false;<br />\r\n$e=12.89;<br />\r\n$f=$a;<br />\r\n$z=$t=$v=&quot;hi&quot;;<br />\r\n引用赋值<br />\r\n$u=&amp;$a;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">变量的作用域<br />\r\n局部变量&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n函数参数&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n全局变量<br />\r\n静态变量<br />\r\n函数参数在退出函数时不销毁</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">可变变量<br />\r\n&lt;?php<br />\r\n$hi=&quot;hello&quot;;<br />\r\n$$hi=&quot;world&quot;;<br />\r\necho &quot;$hi $hello&quot;;<br />\r\necho &quot;$hi ${$hi}&quot;;<br />\r\n?&gt;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>11.6 数据类型</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">Boolean<br />\r\n可以用非0和0来表示true和false<br />\r\n整型<br />\r\n12&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0765&nbsp;&nbsp; 0xC2E&nbsp;&nbsp; -12&nbsp;<br />\r\n浮点数<br />\r\n4.56&nbsp; 4.0&nbsp; 8.9e3&nbsp; 1.23E+11<br />\r\n字符串<br />\r\n可用双引号和单引号作为定界符<br />\r\n单引号内不会解析变量，而双引号会解析变量<br />\r\nNULL<br />\r\n复合数据类型<br />\r\n数组、对象、资源<br />\r\n数据类型转换<br />\r\n自动类型转换<br />\r\n在参与运算时，true转为1,false转为0<br />\r\nNULL参与运算时，转为0<br />\r\ninteger和float在运算时先将integer转为float<br />\r\n字符串和数字运算时，将字符串转为数字<br />\r\n强制类型转换<br />\r\n在要转拘的变量之前加上用括号括起来的目标类型<br />\r\n用转换函数intval()、floatval()和strval()<br />\r\n强制类型转换不会改变被转换变量本身类型，而是通过转换得到新类型数据赋给新变量，原变量的类型和值不变<br />\r\nsettype()可改变原变量的类型<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>11.7 常量</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">用define函数定义常量<br />\r\n预定义常量</p>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/dn8w3o34#ch11_PHP语法基础_01.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch11_PHP语法基础_01.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
 (117,'<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">算术运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">赋值运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">位运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">比较运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">错误控制运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">执行运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">递增／递减运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">逻辑运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">字符串运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">数组运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">类型运算符</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: \'sans serif\', tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">\r\n<div>if</div>\r\n<div>else</div>\r\n<div>elseif/else if</div>\r\n<div>流程控制的替代语法</div>\r\n<div>while</div>\r\n<div>do-while</div>\r\n<div>for</div>\r\n<div>foreach</div>\r\n<div>break</div>\r\n<div>continue</div>\r\n<div>switch</div>\r\n<div>declare</div>\r\n<div>return</div>\r\n<div>require</div>\r\n<div>include</div>\r\n<div>require_once</div>\r\n<div>include_once</div>\r\n<div>goto</div>\r\n</div>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'',0,1,'','array (\n  0 => \n  array (\n    \'fileurl\' => \'http://115.com/file/e6a8ubsh#ch11_PHP语法基础_02.zip\',\n    \'filename\' => \'ch11_PHP语法基础_02.zip\',\n  ),\n)','★★☆☆☆','VIP'),
