 (9,'<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	红帽CEO吉姆&middot;怀特赫斯特曾在采访时说过，<a href=\"http://os.51cto.com/art/201110/296267.htm\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 66, 118); text-decoration: underline; \">没有开源，谷歌和Facebook根本不可能继续存在</a>。而Linux作为开源软件的先驱，它的出现充分体现了互联网的分享精神，也在一定程度上促成了后来的许多互联网巨擘的出现。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	我们不难看出在20年间Linux的发展可谓是翻天覆地的，从开发人数到使用情况都是如此。下面我们就来一起回顾一下Linux的前世今生吧。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; \">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" class=\"fit-image\" src=\"http://www.redwww.com/uploadfile/2011/1103/20111103050447641.jpg\" style=\"border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-color: initial; text-align: center; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; \" title=\"linux【CHN】\" width=\"498\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; text-align: left; \">\r\n	原文出处：<a href=\"http://www.36kr.com/p/57556.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 66, 118); text-decoration: underline; \">http://www.36kr.com/p/57556.html</a></p>\r\n',0,'',0,10000,'show',0,'',0,1,'|0'),
 (10,'<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	本篇文章角度独特，并不像前几篇Ubuntu 11.10 的文章，过于注重软件应用，而是侧重系统设置，仅供参考。</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0); \">一般设置（GNOME Shell ＆ Unity）</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#1，使用GNOME tweak tool 修改系统主题、字体&hellip;&hellip;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	Ubuntu 11.10的&ldquo;系统设置&ndash;外观&rdquo;，只能对系统主题、桌面背景进行调整。我们可以借助Gnome tweak tool 来进行字体、图标主题设置。</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0); \">sudo apt-get install gnome-tweak-tool</span></pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	<br style=\"clear: both; width: 0px; height: 0px; \" />\r\n	#2,GNOME 3.2 屏幕保护程序</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	GNOME 3 没有屏幕保护程序，只是一片黑屏。我们可以使用Xscreensaver：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get remove gnome-screensaver\r\nsudo apt-get install xscreensaver xscreensaver-gl-extra xscreensaver-data-extra</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	安装完毕后，可在菜单中搜索&ldquo;Screensaver&rdquo;,选择自己喜欢的保护程序即可。可在Ubuntu 桌面右上角&ldquo;启动应用程序&rdquo;里面，添加命令&ldquo;xscreensaver -nosplash&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	要想恢复原来设置：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get remove xscreensaver xscreensaver-gl-extra xscreensaver-data-extra\r\nsudo rm /usr/bin/gnome-screensaver-command\r\nsudo apt-get install gnome-screensaver</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#3，安装Syanptic（新立得软件包管理器）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	Syanptic（新立得软件包管理器）没有搭载在Ubuntu 11.10 默认应用里面。我们可以使用下面命令安装：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install synaptic</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#4，禁用&ldquo;Overlay Scrollbars&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	如果不喜欢Overlay Scrollbars，可以使用下面命令移除：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get remove overlay-scrollbar liboverlay-scrollbar3-0.2-0 liboverlay-scrollbar-0.2-0</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	然后重启生效。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	若恢复原来设置，安装上面删除的软件包即可：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install overlay-scrollbar liboverlay-scrollbar3-0.2-0 liboverlay-scrollbar-0.2-0</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	然后重启生效。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#5，启用GNOME 3.2 新功能：存为网络应用、Sushi预览功能</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	Ubuntu 11.10 没有启动GNOME 3.2 新功能：存为网络应用、Sushi预览。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	存为网络应用需要安装GNOME 浏览器Epophany 3.20:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/gnome3\r\nsudo apt-get update\r\nsudo apt-get install epiphany-browser</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	Sushi预览：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install gnome-sushi</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#6，延长电源寿命</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	可安装应用指示器Jupiter来进行相关设置：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/jupiter\r\nsudo apt-get update\r\nsudo apt-get install jupiter</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	若你的电脑为&ldquo;EeePC&rdquo;，则可以安装：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install jupiter-support-eee</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#7，安装 Sun/Oracle Java</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	因JDL 协议移除，目前 Ubuntu 11.10已不能从软件源中安装&rdquo;sun-java6&Prime;，也不能安装Java 7。当然，我们也可以通过下面方法安装：</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	安装OpenJDK:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install openjdk-7-jre</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	或从LFFL PPA 中安装Oracle(Sun) Java 6：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:ferramroberto/java\r\nsudo apt-get update\r\nsudo apt-get install sun-java6-jdk sun-java6-plugin</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#8，修复Nautilus 打开崩溃现象</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	最近很多同学问到一打开Nautilus，就崩溃，无语之极。原因在于右键的&ldquo;在终端中打开&rdquo;这一软件包，移除即可：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get remove nautilus-open-terminal</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	然后重启Nautilus 即可：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nnautilus -q</pre>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; background-color: transparent; \">\r\n	[page]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; background-color: transparent; \">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0); \">GNOME Shell 设置</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#1，修复ALT+F2</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	Ubuntu 11.10 的GNOME Shell环境有时，ALT+F2组合键会失效。我们可以打开&ldquo;系统设置&rdquo;，依次打开&ldquo;键盘-快捷键-系统&rdquo;，在&ldquo;显示运行命令提示符&rdquo;点击&ldquo;Disabled&rdquo;，按住ALT+F2，设置快捷键为&ldquo;ALT+F2&rdquo;即可。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#2，修改GNOME Shell 主题</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	除了GNOME tweak tool 外，还需要安装&ldquo;User theme extension&rdquo;：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/gnome3\r\nsudo apt-get update\r\nsudo apt-get install gnome-shell-extensions-user-theme</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	然后，使用Gnome tweak tool激活即可。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	其他扩展安装可参考文章：<a href=\"http://www.bentutu.com/2011/10/ubuntu-11-10-ppa-install-gnome-3-e/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 66, 118); text-decoration: underline; \" target=\"_blank\">Ubuntu 11.10 PPA安装GNOME 3 扩展</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#3，修复Nautilus菜单选项显示在&ldquo;活动&rdquo;下，显示错乱：</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	如果启动了Zukitwo等透明GNOME Shell主题，就会出现如题所述问题。该问题解决方法只能折中：<br style=\"clear: both; width: 0px; height: 0px; \" />\r\n	a，在&ldquo;GNOME tweak tool&rdquo;里面关闭&ldquo;Have file manager handle the desktop&rdquo;，可以解决这个显示错乱问题，但桌面上不会显示东东了；<br style=\"clear: both; width: 0px; height: 0px; \" />\r\n	b，移除&ldquo;全局菜单&rdquo;，这样就会在Unity下没有全局应用了，这也是个问题。所以。。。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#4，设置GNOME Shell为自动登录环境</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	如果启动了&ldquo;自动登录&rdquo;，Ubuntu 11.10 默认登录环境为Unity。（开启自动登录：系统设置-用户账户，打开&ldquo;自动登录&rdquo;即可。）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	我们可通过下面命令设置&ldquo;自动登录&rdquo;环境为GNOME Shell：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo /usr/lib/lightdm/lightdm-set-defaults -s gnome-shell</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#5，设置&ldquo;GNOME 经典模式&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	大家可通过下面命令安装&ldquo;GNOME fallback&rdquo;:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install gnome-session-fallback\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<p>\r\n	[page]</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0); \">Unity设置</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#1,我们需要借助工具CCSM。如果没有安装，可通过下面命令安装：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install compizconfig-settings-manager</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	打开CCSM，点击&ldquo;Ubuntu Unity PLugin&rdquo;设置相关选项即可。这里不再介绍。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#2，配置 Unity 2D</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	一些 Unity 2D设置需通过工具&ldquo;dconf-editor&rdquo;，通过下面命令安装：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install dconf-tools</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	安装完毕后，按住ALT+F2，输入&ldquo;dconf-editor&rdquo;启动。依次打开&ldquo;com-canonical-uinity-2d&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#3，启用系统托盘（通知区域）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	我们常用的应用如shutter\\jupiter等还是需要系统托盘，可使用下面命令启用系统托盘：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\ngsettings set com.canonical.Unity.Panel systray-whitelist &quot;[&#39;all&#39;]&quot;</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	注销，登录，生效。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#4，禁用全局菜单</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	如果不喜欢&ldquo;全局菜单模式&rdquo;，可以使用下面命令删除：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get remove appmenu-gtk3 appmenu-gtk appmenu-qt</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	重启计算机生效。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	恢复原来设置：</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nsudo apt-get install appmenu-gtk3 appmenu-gtk appmenu-qt</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	重启计算机。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	也可通过其他方法解决禁用全局菜单@<a href=\"http://www.webupd8.org/2011/03/disable-appmenu-global-menu-in-ubuntu.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 66, 118); text-decoration: underline; \" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	#5，重设Unity</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	当发生一些错误时候，实在没法解决了，可以试试恢复Unity 默认设置：</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	-重设Unity 启动器图标:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nunity --reset-icons</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	-重设Unity:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\nunity --reset</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	-重设Compiz:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12px; width: 591px; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; \">\r\ngconftool-2 --recursive-unset /apps/compiz-1\r\nunity --reset</pre>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: transparent; text-indent: 28px; \">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0); \">-本文转自：</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); \"><a href=\"http://www.bentutu.com/2011/10/ubuntu-11-10-%e7%b3%bb%e7%bb%9f%e8%ae%be%e7%bd%ae%e6%8c%87%e5%af%bc/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 66, 118); text-decoration: none; \" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0); \">笨兔兔博客</span></a></span></p>\r\n',0,'',2,10000,'show',0,'',0,1,'|0'),
